{TEXT 320 1 "a" }{TEXT -1 6 " = 2/5" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }
}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 71 "i.e., we will show that the derivatives \+
of cy2f1 and cy2f2 are negative" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}}
{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 49 "dcy2f1 := diff(cy2f1,a);\ndc
