e terms dcy2f1s and dcy2f2s is negative, each of the terms dcy2f1s and
 dcy2f2s is negative " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 
"" {TEXT -1 94 "Hence, each of the terms dcy2f1 and dcy2f2 are negativ
e => cy2f1 and cy2f2 are decreasing (in " }{TEXT 347 1 "a" }{TEXT -1 
1 ")" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 51 "H
ence, the minimum values of cy2f1, cy2f2 occur at " }{TEXT 322 1 "a" }
